  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951520/extras/171bf6b0b8b35497c27c8288ac10ea44.avif?t=1727787692\" width=540 height=268 /></span><br>Bite Night is a comedic first-person horror game that explores the idea of what if the big scary monster was bad at being big and scary. You play as a gas station attendant who must work the night shift in a rural gas station when things start to go bump in the night. You must try to juggle your responsibilities as a worker while dealing with a monster who may be much less scary and more of a pain in the neck but no one knows how many monsters lurk in the night.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951520/extras/bf3682b24a9f323bb078b5aeb021c8e9.avif?t=1727787692\" width=540 height=268 /></span><br><br>Key Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>First Person</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Blend of Comedy and Horror</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Approx: 30mins playtime</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Retro Graphics</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951520/extras/3421036d033ed5aee3f2731a8c7978d1.avif?t=1727787692\" width=540 height=268 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951520/extras/171bf6b0b8b35497c27c8288ac10ea44.avif?t=1727787692\" width=540 height=268 /></span><br>Bite Night is a comedic first-person horror game that explores the idea of what if the big scary monster was bad at being big and scary. You play as a gas station attendant who must work the night shift in a rural gas station when things start to go bump in the night. You must try to juggle your responsibilities as a worker while dealing with a monster who may be much less scary and more of a pain in the neck but no one knows how many monsters lurk in the night.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951520/extras/bf3682b24a9f323bb078b5aeb021c8e9.avif?t=1727787692\" width=540 height=268 /></span><br><br>Key Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>First Person</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Blend of Comedy and Horror</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Approx: 30mins playtime</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Retro Graphics</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951520/extras/3421036d033ed5aee3f2731a8c7978d1.avif?t=1727787692\" width=540 height=268 /></span>",
